# Layout & Design Fidelity

- **Prioritize layout accuracy over design interpretation.** Match spacing, alignment, proportions, and structure exactly as specified or shown.
- **Do not redesign — replicate.** Implement the given design as-is. Avoid "improving" or reinterpreting layouts unless explicitly asked.
